THE GAME
--------

  'Permu' is a Workbench game where you try to match a pattern
shown in the game window in the fewest moves possible. Each time
you click on a tile, all the tiles at the left and all of those
that are on top of that tile will permutate, and the tile you
clicked will change its place with the one located at the upper
left on the board...

  Does that sounds complicated? Maybe, but it's also fun! Play
the game and you'll see!

  Have fun!

FEATURES
--------

-Simple installation: just run the game and play!

-You can choose a game board size you like, from a 4 x 4 board, up
 to a 9 x 9 board size.

-A game you can play while waiting for other tasks to complete...
 or just for fun!

-Small package, the Lha archive is smaller than 50 kilobytes, so
 it doesn't take ages to download ...although, you can play
 another of my Workbench games while downloading this game ;)

-The game plays on the Workbench screen and its window is
 resizeable.

